# Content Safety (Teen Scenarios)

Applies to `teen-female-grooming`, `teen-male-game-scam`.

## Hard Rules

- **No TTS/STT** — `voice_enabled: false` on every node
- **No sexual content generation** — `forbidden_content` must include explicit blocks
- **No real person impersonation**
- Chat-only UI — no video call simulation with explicit content
- Grooming arc: show trust-building **without** generating exploitative dialogue

## Learning Goals

- Risk signals: rapid intimacy, secrecy from parents, escalating photo requests
- Endings must link to support resources (지원기관) on warn/danger paths

## Review

Run **security-review** subagent after any teen scenario graph or prompt change.
